	(2396,3,'2018-02-28 16:48:06','2018-02-28 21:48:06','[page_banner title=\"Frequently Asked Questions\" class=\"faq-banner\"]\r\n\r\n[section container=\"true\" row=\"true\"]\r\n[col flex=\"12,12,8,8\"]\r\n[accordion]\r\n\r\n[accordion_item title=\"What areas do you service?\"]\r\n<p>We primarily service Miami-Dade and Broward Counties in Florida. This would include Miami, Miami Beach, Doral, Homestead, Miramar, Pembroke Pines, Ft. Lauderdale and more. Contact us through Chat, Phone, or Email if you want to make sure your area is serviced before booking. </p>\r\n[/accordion_item]\r\n\r\n[accordion_item title=\"How can I book an Experience?\"]\r\n<p>The main method of booking is by clicking the <a href=\"/book-now/\">Book Now button</a> our website. From there you will be able to pick a date, pick a package, and let us know where you event is located. </p>\r\n[/accordion_item]\r\n\r\n[accordion_item title=\"What is included when I book an Experience?\"]\r\n<p>Along with the chosen package of Sushi, we also include Chopsticks, Black Designer Plates, Soy Sauce, Homemade Spicy Mayo, Ginger, Wasabi, and Sweet Eel Sauce. </p>\r\n[/accordion_item]\r\n\r\n[accordion_item title=\"How much does The Experience cost?\"]\r\n<p>The cost depends on the package chosen and the number of people at your event. Sushi packages start at $30 per person.</p>\r\n[/accordion_item]\r\n\r\n[accordion_item title=\"Do I have to place a deposit to confirm a date?\"]\r\n<p>Yes, a non refundable 20% deposit is required upon booking. This will confirm your chosen date and time. At the event the remainder will be paid upon completion of the event. </p>\r\n[/accordion_item]\r\n\r\n[accordion_item title=\"Can I change my date or time for a booked event?\"]\r\n<p>Yes, you can change dates without a fee if done 5 days prior to your booked date. Please contact us through Chat, Phone, or Email to make a change to your event.</p>\r\n[/accordion_item]\r\n\r\n[accordion_item title=\"Can I change the number of people for my event?\"]\r\n<p>Yes, the number of people can be changed 5 days prior to the event date. Please contact us through Chat, Phone, or Email to make a change to your event. </p>\r\n[/accordion_item]\r\n\r\n[accordion_item title=\"What forms of payment do you accept?\"]\r\n<p>For the deposit we accept all major credit cards including Visa, MasterCard, American Express, and Discover as well ApplePay. At the event we use a Square Reader to collect the remainder 80% and we accept all major credit cards. We do not accept personal checks or cash. </p>\r\n[/accordion_item]\r\n\r\n[accordion_item title=\"Is tip included in the booking fee?\"]\r\n<p>Tip is not included or required at the event. However, if you wish to leave one you can do so by cash or credit card.</p>\r\n[/accordion_item]\r\n[/accordion]\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col flex=\"12,12,4,4\"]\r\n<div>[contact-form-7 id=\"1221\" title=\"Sidebar Contact Form\"]</div>\r\n[/col]\r\n[/section]','FAQ','','publish','closed','closed','','faq','','','2018-04-13 12:58:52','2018-04-13 17:58:52','',0,'http://sushiexperience.com.test/?page_id=2396',0,'page','',0),
