	(2928,3,'2018-04-17 08:31:23','2018-04-17 13:31:23','[section container=\"true\" row=\"true\" class=\"pt100 pb100\" background=\"/bc/wp-content/uploads/the-experience-header-bg.jpg\"]\r\n<h1 class=\"landing-title\">Sushi Catering In South Florida</h1>\r\n[/section]\r\n[text-blocks id=\"book-now\"]\r\n[section container=\"true\" row=\"true\" background=\"/bc/wp-content/uploads/the-sushi-experience-contact-bg.jpg\"]\r\n[col flex=\"12,12,8,8\"]\r\n<h2>Unique Sushi Catering In South Florida</h2>\r\n<p>Looking for a unique catering experience in South Florida like no other? Welcome to The Sushi Experience! We offer Sushi Catering In South Florida, where a private sushi chef drives to your home or event location, prepares mouth-watering sushi creations that are sure to have your guests talking for years to come, cleans up the mess, and departs the location leaving you with just sushi greatness to savor throughout the night. The Sushi Experience has <a href=\"/about-the-experience/\">multiple packages</a> available for you to choose from, meaning we are sure to have a specialty roll to fit almost anyone\'s appetite.</p>\r\n[gallery thumbnail=\"medium\" lightbox=\"services-photo\" xxs=\"2\" xs=\"2\" sm=\"3\" md=\"3\" lg=\"3\" class=\"mt20\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"mt20\">Your In Home Sushi Chef</h3>\r\n<p>Chef Vu is a personable and professional home sushi chef dedicated to providing fresh, hand-rolled sushi while keeping up conversations with you and your guests throughout the night. What makes The Sushi Experience unique is not limited to just our highly talented chef, but also our comprehensive catering solution where plates, utensils, sauces, etc. are all provided, meaning that your only responsibility for the night is filling the room.</p>\r\n<p>Chef Vu has a diverse background which aided in the development of his masterful sushi catering and private event planning skills. Chef Vu comes from a Vietnamese family culture, making all of his traditional Vietnamese dishes and Sushi creations from scratch. Learn more about Chef Vu today on the <a href=\"/meet-the-chef/\">Meet The Chef</a> page!</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"mt20\">A Private Sushi Chef For Any Occasion!</h3>\r\n<p>The Sushi Experience specializes in private events, corporate events, & private parties. We are capable of providing full-service Sushi Catering South Florida packages for retirement parties, bachelor & bachelorette parties, fundraisers, team building activities, birthday parties, graduation parties, weddings, & much more! Don\'t see a package that you like? No problem! Custom packages are available at checkout and can be mixed with any of our delicious Sushi Rolls or Nigris creations.</p>\r\n[/col]\r\n[col flex=\"12,12,4,4\"]\r\n<div class=\"video-container mb40\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3yjMvWiIpjY\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"1221\" title=\"Sidebar Contact Form\"]\r\n[/col]\r\n[/section]','Sushi Catering In South Florida','','publish','closed','closed','','sushi-catering-in-south-florida','','','2018-04-17 08:31:23','2018-04-17 13:31:23','',0,'http://sushiexperience.com.test/?page_id=2928',0,'page','',0),
